cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.SI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with caching and coded multicasting, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of caching also involves data structures (cs.DS) and the optimization of delivery schemes can be seen as a machine learning problem (cs.LG). Finally, the paper presents a decentralized approach, which is related to distributed systems (cs.SI).
